00:56:37.550 --> 00:56:39.770
are in the 2,000 words.

00:56:39.770 --> 00:56:43.820
Like energy, for example, and
force is in the top 2,000,

00:56:43.820 --> 00:56:44.680
and so on.

00:56:44.680 --> 00:56:47.460
And so 2,000 words is
